    • Method Detail

      • readObjects

        public TabularParseResult<T> readObjects(java.io.Reader csvReader)

        Translates the given CSV content into a List of objects.

        Translation of each row into its representative object is handled by the RowTranslator provided during construction. This class only handles the generic iteration logic and global error handling.

        Warning: the given CSV content is read completely into memory while parsing. This method does not therefore support very large CSV files (i.e., 50MB+).

        Parameters:
        csvReader - a Reader providing the CSV content. This method will close the reader when done.
